A vintage 1950s illustration style scene showing five identical men in gray suits sitting around an enormous ornate roulette wheel, each clutching thick stacks of documents and blueprints. The wheel's segments contain miniature architectural models and complex machinery instead of numbers. Golden coins cascade from their briefcases onto the floor while a massive hourglass looms in the background, sand nearly depleted. The color palette features muted teals, mustard yellows, and warm browns with subtle paper texture throughout. The men's expressions show a mixture of exhaustion and desperate hope as they watch the wheel spin, their documents scattered and crumpled around them like fallen leaves.
